	(11, 1, 2, 'wrapper', 'webpage', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en-US\">\n\n<head>\n    {_head}\n</head>\n\n<body class=\"home page-template-default page page-id-1465 wp-embed-responsive elementor-default elementor-kit-3 elementor-page elementor-page-1465 menu-ani-1 hover-ani-1 is-rm-1 is-hd-1 is-backtop none-m-backtop is-mstick sync-bookmarks\" data-theme=\"default\">\n\n<div class=\"site-outer\">\n    <header id=\"site-header\" class=\"header-wrap rb-section header-template\">\n        {embed=layout/_header}\n    </header>', NULL, 1680996695, 1, 'n', 0, '', 'n', 'n', 'o', 0, 'n', 'y'),
	(13, 1, 2, '_post_details', 'webpage', '\n<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-970a442 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"970a442\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"></div>\n    <div class=\"single-standard-5 is-sidebar-right sticky-sidebar optimal-line-length elementor-container pb-90 elementor-column-gap-custom\">\n        <div id=\"post-16\" class=\"post-16 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-wildlife-watch tag-hot\">\n\n            <div class=\"rb-container edge-padding\">\n                <div class=\"grid-container\">\n                    <div class=\"s-ct\">\n                        <div class=\"s-ct-wrap\">\n                            <div class=\"s-ct-inner\">\n                                <div class=\"e-ct-outer\">\n                                    <div class=\"entry-content rbct clearfix is-highlight-shares\" itemprop=\"articleBody\">\n                                        <p class=\"has-drop-cap\">The feline has also brought attention to the need for <a\n                                                href=\"#\">wildlife corridors to connect animal</a> populations through\n                                            highly urbanized southern California. Such sprawl isolates pockets of\n                                            mountain lions, which can lead to inbreeding.</p>\n\n                                        <div class=\"ruby-table-contents rbtoc table-fw\">\n                                            <div class=\"toc-header\"><i class=\"rbi rbi-read\"></i><span\n                                                    class=\"h3\">Contents</span><a class=\"ruby-toc-toggle\" href=\"#\"><i\n                                                        class=\"rbi rbi-angle-down\"></i></a></div>\n                                            <div class=\"inner\"><a href=\"#a-safer-world-for-animals-and-people\"\n                                                    class=\"table-link anchor-link h5\" data-index=\"rb-heading-index-0\">A\n                                                    safer world for animals and people</a><a\n                                                    href=\"#bear-baiting-banned-in-alaskan-preserves\"\n                                                    class=\"table-link anchor-link h5\"\n                                                    data-index=\"rb-heading-index-1\">Bear baiting banned in Alaskan\n                                                    preserves</a><a\n                                                    href=\"#what-is-the-difference-between-a-lion-and-a-tiger\"\n                                                    class=\"table-link anchor-link h5\"\n                                                    data-index=\"rb-heading-index-2\">What is the difference between a\n                                                    lion and a tiger?</a><a\n                                                    href=\"#youll-help-protect-vulnerable-communities\"\n                                                    class=\"table-link anchor-link h5\"\n                                                    data-index=\"rb-heading-index-3\">You’ll help protect vulnerable\n                                                    communities</a><a href=\"#facts-about-red-panda\"\n                                                    class=\"table-link anchor-link h5\"\n                                                    data-index=\"rb-heading-index-4\">Facts about red panda</a><a\n                                                    href=\"#breaking-down-the-barriers\" class=\"table-link anchor-link h5\"\n                                                    data-index=\"rb-heading-index-5\">Breaking down the barriers</a></div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <p>Optimization for various types of devices and resolutions plays a fundamental\n                                            role in modern website design. Web page layouts should be <a href=\"#\"\n                                                target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">genuinely responsive</a> and\n                                            not rely on any fixed-size elements. Web designers using <a href=\"#\"\n                                                target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">fluid grids</a> and flexible\n                                            images will guarantee that a web page will render well on a variety of\n                                            devices, windows, and screen sizes.</p>\n                                        <figure class=\"wp-block-pullquote\">\n                                            <blockquote>\n                                                <p>As far as the laws of mathematics refer to reality, they are not\n                                                    certain; and as far as they are certain, they do not refer to\n                                                    reality.</p><cite>Albert Einstein</cite>\n                                            </blockquote>\n                                        </figure>\n                                        <p>Most users search for something interesting<em> </em>(or useful) and\n                                            clickable; as soon as some promising candidates are found, users\n                                            click.<strong> If the new page doesn’t meet users’ expectations,</strong>\n                                            the back button is clicked and the search process is continued.</p>\n                                        <h2 id=\"a-safer-world-for-animals-and-people\"\n                                            class=\"rb-heading-index-0 wp-block-heading\">A safer world for animals and\n                                            people</h2>\n                                        <p>Not all websites are made equal. Some websites are simple, logical, and easy\n                                            to use. Others are a messy hodgepodge of pages and links.</p>\n                                        <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"\n                                                width=\"1000\" height=\"657\"\n                                                src=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as1.jpg\"\n                                                alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3006\"\n                                                srcset=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as1.jpg 1000w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as1-300x197.jpg 300w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as1-768x505.jpg 768w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as1-860x565.jpg 860w\"\n                                                sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\">\n                                            <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">How are innovations in robotics\n                                                changing the way we perceive the world?</figcaption>\n                                        </figure>\n                                        <p>Without website navigation, your visitors can’t figure out how to find your\n                                            blog, your email signup page, your product listings, pricing, contact\n                                            information, or help docs.</p>\n                                        <div class=\"related-sec related-3\">\n                                            <div class=\"inner block-small block-hrc hrc-1\">\n                                                <div class=\"block-h heading-layout-10\">\n                                                    <div class=\"heading-inner\">\n                                                        <h4 class=\"heading-title\"><span>More Read</span></h4>\n                                                    </div>\n                                                </div>\n                                                <div class=\"block-inner\">\n                                                    <div class=\"p-wrap p-grid p-grid-1\" data-pid=\"35\">\n                                                        <div class=\"feat-holder overlay-text\">\n                                                            <div class=\"p-featured\">\n                                                                <a class=\"p-flink\"\n                                                                    href=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/hungry-bear-comes-out-of-hibernation-looking-for-food/\"\n                                                                    title=\"Hungry Bear Comes Out of Hibernation Looking For Food\">\n                                                                    <img width=\"330\" height=\"220\"\n                                                                        src=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2023/02/a7-330x220.jpg\"\n                                                                        class=\"featured-img wp-post-image\" alt=\"\"\n                                                                        decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"> </a>\n                                                            </div>\n                                                        </div>\n                                                        <h4 class=\"entry-title\"> <a class=\"p-url\"\n                                                                href=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/hungry-bear-comes-out-of-hibernation-looking-for-food/\"\n                                                                rel=\"bookmark\">Hungry Bear Comes Out of Hibernation\n                                                                Looking For Food</a></h4>\n                                                    </div>\n                                                    <div class=\"p-wrap p-list-inline\" data-pid=\"71\">\n                                                        <h6 class=\"entry-title\"><i class=\"rbi rbi-plus\"></i> <a\n                                                                class=\"p-url\"\n                                                                href=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/learn-how-to-take-proper-care-of-lovebirds-before-you-own/\"\n                                                                rel=\"bookmark\">Learn How to Take Proper Care of\n                                                                Lovebirds Before You Own</a></h6>\n                                                    </div>\n                                                    <div class=\"p-wrap p-list-inline\" data-pid=\"67\">\n                                                        <h6 class=\"entry-title\"><i class=\"rbi rbi-plus\"></i> <a\n                                                                class=\"p-url\"\n                                                                href=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/how-fast-can-a-leopard-run-average-speed/\"\n                                                                rel=\"bookmark\">How Fast Can a Leopard Run (Average\n                                                                Speed)</a></h6>\n                                                    </div>\n                                                    <div class=\"p-wrap p-list-inline\" data-pid=\"45\">\n                                                        <h6 class=\"entry-title\"><i class=\"rbi rbi-plus\"></i> <a\n                                                                class=\"p-url\"\n                                                                href=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/all-23-types-of-foxes-and-where-to-see-them-in-the-wild/\"\n                                                                rel=\"bookmark\">All 23 Types of Foxes and Where to See\n                                                                Them in the Wild</a></h6>\n                                                    </div>\n                                                </div>\n                                            </div>\n                                        </div>\n                                        <p><strong>Quick and easy access to the content they’re after is more important\n                                                for your website users than a… visually-stunning design.</strong></p>\n                                        <p>Website navigation allows visitors to flow from one page to another without\n                                            frustration. If you’ve done your job well, visitors leave your site with the\n                                            <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">intention to\n                                                return</a> and might even buy something from you or sign up for your\n                                            email list.</p>\n                                        <p><em>Bad navigation is an especially common problem. We’ve all struggled to\n                                                find things on disorganized websites without any logical structure. It\n                                                feels hopeless.</em></p>\n                                        <p>Using <strong>“complex large pictures”</strong>. Because a carousel generally\n                                            carries a lot of picture messages, complex large pictures result in low\n                                            performance and <strong>“slow loading rate”</strong> of the sites,\n                                            especially those whose first homepages are occupied by high-resolution\n                                            carousels.</p>\n                                        <h2 id=\"bear-baiting-banned-in-alaskan-preserves\"\n                                            class=\"rb-heading-index-1 wp-block-heading\"><strong>Bear baiting banned in\n                                                Alaskan preserves</strong></h2>\n                                        <p>In design, rhythm is created by simply repeating elements in predictable\n                                            patterns. This repetition is a natural thing that occurs everywhere in our\n                                            world. As people, we are driven everyday by predictable, timed events.</p>\n                                        <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"\n                                                width=\"1000\" height=\"667\"\n                                                src=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as2.jpg\"\n                                                alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3007\"\n                                                srcset=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as2.jpg 1000w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as2-330x220.jpg 330w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as2-420x280.jpg 420w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as2-615x410.jpg 615w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2022/12/as2-860x574.jpg 860w\"\n                                                sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\">\n                                            <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Success is no accident. It is hard\n                                                work, perseverance, learning, studying, sacrifice and most of all, love\n                                                of what you are doing.</figcaption>\n                                        </figure>\n                                        <p>One of the best ways to use <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\"\n                                                rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">repetition and rhythm in web design</a> is in\n                                            the site’s navigation menu. A consistent, easy-to-follow pattern—in color,\n                                            layout, etc. Gives users an intuitive roadmap to everything you want to\n                                            share on your site.</p>\n                                        <p>Rhythm also factors into the <strong>layout of content</strong>. For example,\n                                            you <strong>“might have”</strong> blog articles, press releases, and events\n                                            each follow their own certain layout pattern.</p>\n                                        <h2 id=\"what-is-the-difference-between-a-lion-and-a-tiger\"\n                                            class=\"rb-heading-index-2 wp-block-heading\">What is the difference between a\n                                            lion and a tiger?</h2>\n                                        <p>Nobody enjoys looking at an ugly web page. cluttered images and distracting\n                                            animation can all turn customers <strong>“off”</strong> and send them\n                                            shopping<strong> “somewhere else”</strong>. Basic composition rules to\n                                            create more effective:</p>\n                                        <ul class=\"rb-list\">\n                                            <li>Direct the Eye With<strong> </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\n                                                    href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">Leading Lines</a></li>\n                                            <li>Balance Out Your Elements</li>\n                                            <li>Use Elements That<strong> Complement Each Other</strong></li>\n                                            <li>Be clear about your <strong>“focal points”</strong> and where you place\n                                                them</li>\n                                        </ul>\n                                        <p>The size and position of elements in a composition will determine its\n                                            balance. An unbalanced design generates tension, which may be the goal in\n                                            many design projects, but for web apps that demand repeated comfortable use,\n                                            tension is not a desirable trait.</p>\n                                        <h2 id=\"youll-help-protect-vulnerable-communities\"\n                                            class=\"rb-heading-index-3 wp-block-heading\">You’ll help protect vulnerable\n                                            communities</h2>\n                                        <p><strong>UX and UI: </strong>Two terms that are often used interchangeably,\n                                            but actually mean very different things. <em>So what exactly is the\n                                                difference?</em></p>\n                                        \n                                        <p>UX design refers to the term <em>“user experience design”</em>, while UI\n                                            stands for <em>“user interface design</em><strong>”</strong>. Both elements\n                                            are crucial to a product and work closely together. But despite their\n                                            relationship, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">the\n                                                roles themselves</a> are quite different.</p>\n                                        <h2 id=\"facts-about-red-panda\" class=\"rb-heading-index-4 wp-block-heading\">\n                                            <strong><em>Facts about red panda</em></strong></h2>\n                                        <p>Good design guides the user by communicating purpose and priority. For that\n                                            reason, every part of the design should be based on an\n                                            <strong>“<strong>informed decision</strong></strong>” rather than an\n                                            arbitrary result of personal taste or the current trend.</p>\n                                        <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"\n                                                width=\"1024\" height=\"717\"\n                                                src=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2023/02/a8-1024x717.jpg\"\n                                                alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2942\"\n                                                srcset=\"https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2023/02/a8-1024x717.jpg 1024w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2023/02/a8-300x210.jpg 300w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2023/02/a8-768x538.jpg 768w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2023/02/a8-860x602.jpg 860w, https://foxiz.themeruby.com/animals/wp-content/uploads/sites/7/2023/02/a8.jpg 1200w\"\n                                                sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\">\n                                            <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Study nature. Love nature. Stay close\n                                                to nature. It will never fail you.</figcaption>\n                                        </figure>\n                                        <p>Provide distinct styles for interactive elements, such as <em>links and\n                                                buttons</em>, to make them easy to identify. For example,\n                                            <strong>“change the appearance of links”</strong> on mouse hover, “keyboard\n                                            focus”, and “touch-screen activation”.</p>\n                                        <h2 id=\"breaking-down-the-barriers\" class=\"rb-heading-index-5 wp-block-heading\">\n                                            Breaking down the barriers</h2>\n                                        <p><strong>Design is not the end-all solution to all of the worlds\n                                                problems</strong> — but with the right thinking and application, it can\n                                            definitely be a good beginning to start tackling them.</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <div class=\"efoot\">\n                                        <div class=\"efoot-bar tag-bar\">\n                                            <span class=\"blabel is-meta\"><i class=\"rbi rbi-tag\"\n                                                    aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>TAGGED:</span>\n                                            <span class=\"tags-list h5\"><a\n                                                    hre